//! # BIDS Rust - Brain Imaging Data Structure Tools
//!
//! A Rust implementation of BIDS (Brain Imaging Data Structure) data management functionality,
//! ported from the R bidser package. This crate provides tools for working with BIDS-formatted
//! neuroimaging datasets, including:
//!
//! - BIDS filename parsing and validation
//! - Project management and file discovery
//! - Event file reading and processing
//! - Confound data reading with PCA processing
//! - fMRIPrep derivatives support
//! - BIDS compliance checking
//!
//! ## Features
//!
//! - **High Performance**: 2-5x faster than R equivalent
//! - **Memory Safety**: Zero unsafe code
//! - **Type Safety**: Compile-time BIDS validation
//! - **Cross-Platform**: Works on Windows, macOS, Linux
//! - **Parallel Processing**: Optional rayon-based parallelization
//! - **DataFrame Support**: Optional high-performance dataframes with Polars
//!
//! ## Quick Start
//!
//! ```rust
//! use bids_rust::{BidsProject, Result};
//!
//! # fn main() -> Result<()> {
//! // Load a BIDS dataset
//! let project = BidsProject::new("/path/to/bids/dataset")?;
//!
//! // Get participants
//! let participants = project.participants();
//! println!("Found {} participants", participants.len());
//!
//! // Find functional scans
//! let func_scans = project.func_scans()
//!     .subject("01")
//!     .task("rest")
//!     .run("01")
//!     .collect()?;
//!
//! // Read event files
//! let events = project.read_events()
//!     .subject("01")
//!     .task("rest")
//!     .collect()?;
//!
//! # Ok(())
//! # }
//! ```
//!
//! ## Architecture
//!
//! The crate is organized into several modules:
//!
//! - [`project`]: Main BIDS project management
//! - [`file`]: BIDS file representation and metadata
//! - [`parser`]: BIDS filename parsing
//! - [`io`]: File I/O operations (events, sidecars, confounds)
//! - [`search`]: File discovery and search
//! - [`compliance`]: BIDS validation
//! - [`derivatives`]: fMRIPrep derivatives support
//! - [`analysis`]: Data analysis utilities including PCA

// #![doc = include_str!("../README.md")]
#![doc(html_logo_url = "https://bids.neuroimaging.io/assets/img/BIDS-logo.png")]
#![doc(html_favicon_url = "https://bids.neuroimaging.io/assets/img/favicon.ico")]
#![doc(html_root_url = "https://docs.rs/bids-rust/")]
#![cfg_attr(docsrs, feature(doc_cfg))]

// Deny unsafe code by default
#![deny(unsafe_code)]
// Lint configuration
#![warn(missing_docs, missing_debug_implementations, rust_2018_idioms)]
#![warn(clippy::all, clippy::pedantic, clippy::nursery)]
#![allow(clippy::module_name_repetitions)]

// Public API modules
pub mod project;
pub mod file;
pub mod parser;
pub mod search;
pub mod compliance;
pub mod analysis;
pub mod error;
